My theory of the MV:
Accepting yourself.

Each of the scenes play a role in this theory, enjoy :D

Yeji: She represents you learning to have fun, enjoy, and express yourself.

Yuna: She represents you to not always need to be perfect.

Lia: She represents when you make mistakes.

Chaeryoung: Represents people judging you but you quickly turn them down.

Ryujin: Represents you having your own style and not caring about what others say.

I hope u enjoyed my theory. It’s kinda rushed and stupid but I kinda like it :D
